title: May the Force Be With You
text: Reaction: After you commit a unit to the Force, remove all focus tokens from that unit.

title: Yoda
text:
Elite.
This unit gains [Unit Damage] for each point on the Death Star dial.

title: Dagobah Nudj
text:
Reaction: After this unit enters play decrease the Death Star dial by 1.
Forced Interrupt: When this unit leaves play increase the Death Star dial by 1.

title: Dagobah Training Grounds
text:
Enhance your play area.
Limited. (You cannot play more than one limited card each turn.)

keywords.text: You cannot play more than one limited card each turn.

title: Yoda, You Seek Yoda
text: Action: Increase the Death Star dial by 1 to search your deck for Yoda, and put him into play, if able.

title: Seeds of Decay
text: You may place 1 focus token on a target ready unit that is committed to the Force.

title: Behind Enemy Lines
text: Reaction: After an objective enters play, look at the top card of an opponent's objective or command deck. You may move that card to the bottom of its deck.

title: Winter
text: Reaction: After you win a Force struggle, return a target enemy enhancement to the top of its owner's deck.

title: Tactical Genius
text: Reaction: After this unit enters play, remove 1 focus token from a target unit committed to the Force.

title: Observation Point
text:
Enhance your play area.
Action: Focus this enhancement to look at the top card of each player's deck. Then you may discard 1 of those cards.

title: Hidden Outpost
text:
Enhance your play area.
Limited. (You cannot play more than one limited card per turn.)

keywords.text: You cannot play more than one limited card per turn.

title: Infiltration
text: Action: During an engagement, put a Character unit into play from your hand as a participating unit on your side. If that unit is still in play at the end of the phase, return it to your hand.

title: The Second Phase
text:
Sith affiliation only.
Action: Damage this objective to reduce the cost of the next [Sith] unit you play this phase by 1. (Limit once per phase.)

title: Dark Trooper Legion
text: Interrupt: When you play this unit from your hand, deal 1 damage each to any number of your objectives to reduce the cost of this unit by 1 for each damage dealt.

title: Dark Trooper Legion
text: Interrupt: When you play this unit from your hand, deal 1 damage each to any number of your objectives to reduce the cost of this unit by 1 for each damage dealt.

title: Force Shield
text:
Enhance a [Sith] objective.
Interrupt: When enhanced objective is destroyed, draw 2 cards. If the Balance of the Force is with the dark side, draw 3 cards instead.

title: Facility Repair
text: Reaction: After a [Sith] objective is dealt damage, remove 1 damage from that objective. Then, place 1 shield on that objective.

title: Consumed by the Dark Side
text:
Play only in the Balance of the Force is with the dark side.
Action: Remove up to 1 damage from each objective you control.

title: Reinforcements
text: Reaction: After this objective enters play, put the topmost [Imperial Navy] unit in your discard pile into play, committed to the Force. (If that unit cannot be committed to the Force, this effect cannot initiate.)

title: Reserve Troopers
text:
Targeted Strike.
This unit cannot be declared as an attacker or defender unless it is committed to the Force.

text:

title: Security Checkpoint
text:
Enhance your play area.
Each unit you control that is committed to the Force gains edge (1).

title: Award Ceremony
text:
Play only if you have at least 1 Force card in your supply.
Action: Put an [Imperial Navy] Character unit into play from your hand. Then, commit that unit to the Force.

title: Echoes of the Force
text: You may commit a target unit to or remove a target unit from the Force.

title: The Scavengers
text: Reaction: After this objective enters play, destroy all units in play.

title: Wittin
text:
While this unit is committed to the Force, it cannot be damaged or destroyed.
Forced Reaction: After you lose a Force struggle, remove this unit from the Force, if able.

title: Jawa Scrap Dealers
text: Reaction: After a friendly unit is destroyed, put this unit into play from your hand.

title: Jawa Scrap Dealers
text: Reaction: After a friendly unit is destroyed, put this unit into play from your hand.

title: Watchful Eyes
text: Action: Look at the top 2 cards of an objective deck. You may move 1 of those cards to the bottom of its deck. Return the other cards to the top of the deck in any order.
